<div class="module">
<h3>Treatments and services offered at the Gastrointestinal and Liver services department </h3>
</div>
<ul>
<li>Alcohol related liver disease</li>
<li>Balloon enteroscopy</li>
<li>Biopsy / fine needle aspiration</li>
<li>Co-infection (HIV with hepatitis B and/or C) cirrhosis</li>
<li>Colonoscopy flexible sigmoidoscopy</li>
<li>Endoscopic ultrasound</li>
<li>Family clinic</li>
<li>Fatty liver disease</li>
<li>Hepatitis B and C</li>
<li>Liver transplant service</li>
<li>Manometry Therapeutic colonoscopy</li>
<li>Oesophageal, duodenal, biliary and colonic palliative stenting</li>
<li>Pregnancy and liver disease</li>
<li>Radiofrequency ablation of Barrett's Oesophagus</li>
<li>Therapeutic colonoscopy</li>
<li>Upper gastrointestinal endoscopy</li>
<li>Video capsule enteroscopy</li>
</ul>
